high_descs: Walk forward, then left to the sink on the right
Pick up the knife from the sink
Turn to the left where the potato is
Slice the potato with the knife
Turn back to the sink
Place the knife in the sink
Turn to the left, where the sliced potatoes are
Pick up one of the slices of potato
Turn to the left, walk to the microwave on the right
Open the microwave, place the potato slice in, warm, open the door and remove the potato
Turn to the right, walk to the sink
Place the sliced potato in the sink
anns.task_desc: slice and heat a potato chip

high_descs: Turn left and go to the sink
Grab the knife out of the sink
Turn left and look at the counter
Slice the potato on the counter
Turn right and look at the sink
Put the knife down to the left of the sink
Turn left and look at the counter
Grab a slice of potato off of the counter
Turn left and go to the microwave
Heat the potato slice in the microwave and then take it out
Turn around and go to the sink
Put the potato slice in the sink
anns.task_desc: Putting a hot potato slice in the sink

high_descs: Hang a left at the fridge and walk to the sink on the right.
Pick up the silver knife from the sink.
Turn left and walk to the counter.
Slice the potato on the counter to the far right.
Turn right to face the sink.
Put the silver knife on the left side of the counter on top of the sharp knife.
Turn left to face the counter.
Pick up a slice of potato from the counter.
Turn left and walk to the silver stove on the right.
Put the slice of potato inside the microwave, heat it, remove it and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the sink on the left.
Put the cooked slice of potato inside the sink to the right of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked slice of potato in a sink.
